    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 114.</p><p>Blasphemous Hand</p><p>Strike, Dainsleif</p><p>Weapon: Unarmed strike Classes: Barbarian, Fighter, Monk Channeling Time: 1 action Base LP Cost: 0 LP Range: 5 feet Duration: Instantaneous</p><p>You forgo the need for a weapon, sullying your hand with blasphemous energy. Make a single unarmed strike against a target within reach. On a hit, your strike plunges into the target’s soul, absorbing their essence. The target must succeed on a Constitution saving throw against your Mythical Technique save DC or take 20d6 Dark damage. On a successful save, the target takes half damage. You gain temporary hit points equal to the damage dealt.</p></div>",
